cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL 

This paper focuses on image annotation, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves deep learning models, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of social tags for refining visual features suggests a possible connection to natural language processing (cs.CL). The title also mentions "multi-modal" and "multi-scale", which could indicate a focus on multimodal learning (cs.MM). Finally, the paper deals with the issue of annotating images with an automatically-determined number of class labels, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
